              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Assistance of 100% of the course fee for students belonging to SC/ST, Economically weaker sections (criteria based). 40% seats would be reserved for the students belonging to these categories."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Assistance to be provided only after a candidate clears a certification exam NIELIT or SSCs or a certifying body recognised by SSCs "
